       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. FEEPOST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY CUSTOMER.
       01  MONTHLY-FEE PIC S9(3)V99 COMP-3 VALUE 5.00.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           PERFORM 1000-CALCULATE-FEE.
           PERFORM 2000-WRITE-POSTING.
           GOBACK.
       1000-CALCULATE-FEE.
           IF ACCOUNT-ACTIVE
              SUBTRACT MONTHLY-FEE FROM ACCOUNT-BALANCE
           END-IF.
       2000-WRITE-POSTING.
           DISPLAY 'POST MONTHLY FEE FOR ' CUSTOMER-ID.

